    <description>A simple ASP.NET MVC3 helper for Gravatar providing extension methods to HtmlHelper and UrlHelper. Example usage: @Html.GravatarImage("MyEmailAddress@example.com", 80, new { Title = "My Gravatar", Alt = "Gravatar" })</description>
    <summary>A simple ASP.NET MVC3 helper for Gravatar.</summary>
    <releaseNotes>- Fix the position of the optional file extension to be in the correct place within the URL.
- Make GravatarHelper.MinImageSize and GravatarHelper.MaxImageSize public.
- Reference MVC3 assemblies instead of MVC2.
- Introduced unit tests.
- Introduced StyleCop.</releaseNotes>
